  "body": "With 0.8, we finally have a stable ground to work on and optimize our beacon chain implementations. It will be great if we can clarify what has actually been frozen, so that we can have more peace of mind when creating structures not defined in spec.\r\n\r\nWhat is frozen:\r\n\r\n- Beacon state transition function (`specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md`)\r\n- Beacon fork choice rule (`specs/core/0_fork-choice.md`)\r\n- Ssz merkleization (`specs/simple-serialize.md#merkleization`)\r\n\r\nWhat is not frozen:\r\n\r\n- BLS\r\n- Ssz serialization (`specs/simple-serialize.md#serialization`)\r\n- Networking\r\n- Deposit contract",
